name: Stock Deduction Reports
query:
select 
      challan_no as "Challan No",
      item_code as "Challan Part No",
      challan_date as "Challan Date" ,
      challan_value As "Challan Value",
      qty as "Challan Qty",
      ded_qty as "Invoice Qty",
      rem_qty as "Remaining Qty"
from viewStock
